  "texts": [
    "**Ongoing Refinement** My training includes feedback loops where my responses are evaluated for accuracy, clarity, and safety.",
    "This helps me improve over time and avoid spreading misinformation --especially important in finance, where errors can have real consequences.",
    "---### Important Limitation: While I can simulate reasoning and provide well-informed insights, I don't \"understand\" in the human sense.",
    "I don't have beliefs, experiences, or emotions.",
    "My \"reasoning\" is based on statistical patterns in data, not personal judgment."
  ]
}